{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"607a4311-156f-4a67-9298-161930371b71","content":"Use the `--filter` option with `ClassName`:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --filter \"ClassName=Contoso.Reports.Tests.ReportExporterTests\"\n```\n\nOr the shorter form using just the class name:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --filter \"ClassName~ReportExporterTests\"\n```\n\n- `=` matches the fully qualified name exactly.\n- `~` does a contains match, so the short class name suffices.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d7fe7156-77ab-4570-a5b1-f3ffae14329a","outputTokens":108,"requestId":"9820:3C606F:1D17EA:265D11:69FFDDEB"},"id":"6501c3a7-8135-4445-8a1c-e14c5a1153c6","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:22:55.403Z","parentId":"930ea2f8-b205-4c60-9b38-5fb9cbb8801a"}
